data.description: Welcome to your dream home in desirable Westmont! This spacious and beautifully designed townhouse features three bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and a full basement for all your storage needs. The home boasts unique skylights that fill the space with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Step outside to enjoy the newly paved driveway and deck, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. Inside, you'll find all new light fixtures, a newly added third bedroom, and updated features throughout, including a new shower and tile in the master bathroom, a new fireplace, and new kitchen countertops and sink.  Other highlights include LVT floors upstairs, a freshly painted garage, and the convenience of HOA-managed landscaping and snow removal. The kitchen appliances and washer are only two years old, ensuring a modern and efficient living experience.  This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a truly special property in a prime location!
